70.Redmine98465:修改STK名称从SIM卡中读取？

解决方案：#98465
修改STK名称从卡中获取
    alps/frameworks/opt/telephony/src/java/com/android/internal/telephony/cat/CommandParamsFactory.java
        if(com.mediatek.common.featureoption.FeatureOption.SAGEREAL_VODAFONE_AU_STKNAME){
            if(!is_item_select){
                android.os.SystemProperties.set("gsm.sim.operator.sume", menu.title==null?"":menu.title);   //保存STK中的名称到 gsm.sim.operator.sume
            }
        }
    alps/frameworks/opt/telephony/src/java/com/android/internal/telephony/gsm/GsmServiceStateTracker.java
        if(com.mediatek.common.featureoption.FeatureOption.SAGEREAL_VODAFONE_AU_STKNAME){
            try {
                PackageManager pm = mPhone.getContext().getPackageManager();
                if(pm.getApplicationEnabledSetting("com.android.stk") == PackageManager.COMPONENT_ENABLED_STATE_DEFAULT){
                    pm.setApplicationEnabledSetting("com.android.stk", PackageManager.COMPONENT_ENABLED_STATE_DISABLED, PackageManager.DONT_KILL_APP);
                }
                pm.setApplicationEnabledSetting("com.android.stk", PackageManager.COMPONENT_ENABLED_STATE_DEFAULT, PackageManager.DONT_KILL_APP);
            } catch (Exception e) {
                e.printStackTrace();
            }
        }
    alps/frameworks/base/core/java/android/app/ApplicationPackageManager.java
        //修改 getText() 方法，修改获取应用名称的方法
        if(com.mediatek.common.featureoption.FeatureOption.SAGEREAL_VODAFONE_AU_STKNAME){
            try {
                if ("com.android.stk".equalsIgnoreCase(packageName)) {
                    String tmptext0 = SystemProperties.get("gsm.sim.operator.sume", "");
                    String tmptext2 = SystemProperties.get(TelephonyProperties.PROPERTY_OPERATOR_ALPHA_2);
                    if (!tmptext0.isEmpty() && tmptext2.isEmpty() ) {
                        if (!tmptext0.equalsIgnoreCase("com.android.stk")) {
                            text = tmptext0;
                        }
                    } else if (tmptext0.isEmpty() && !tmptext2.isEmpty()) {
                        if (!tmptext2.equalsIgnoreCase("com.android.stk")) {
                            text = tmptext2;
                        }
                    } else {
                        Log.w("PackageManager", "Failure retrieving text 0x" + Integer.toHexString(resid) + " in package " + packageName);
                    }
                }
            } catch (RuntimeException e) {
                Log.w("PackageManager", "Failure retrieving text 0x" + Integer.toHexString(resid) + " in package " + packageName, e);
            }
        }

71. Redmine86490: [客户反馈]Notification : We should be able to remove them by press on the left direction key , as done in appplication historic

解决方案：
把状态栏上的通知栏修改为通过左右键可以移除通知信息
alps/frameworks/base/packages/SystemUI/src/com/android/systemui/statusbar/BaseStatusBar.java
    row.setOnKeyListener(new OnKeyListener() {
        @Override
        public boolean onKey(View v, int keyCode, KeyEvent event) {
            if(event.getAction() == KeyEvent.ACTION_DOWN && (keyCode == KeyEvent.KEYCODE_DPAD_LEFT || keyCode == KeyEvent.KEYCODE_DPAD_RIGHT)){
                if(mPile.canChildBeDismissed(v)){
                    mPile.dismissRowAnimated(v);    //移除通知
                }
                return true;
            }
            return false;
        }
    });

72. Redmine86489:[客户反馈]In a field to input text, when pressing keys, could we have the letters that come out first, and the number after?

解决方案：
修改输入法的顺序：大写字母 + 小写字母 + 数字
目前修改为在 toString() 的时候控制，方便后续修改
alps/frameworks/base/core/java/android/text/method/WordResource.java
    class Word {
        private String wordLower;
        private String wordCapital;
        private String wordSpecielLower;
        private String wordSpecielCapital;
        private String wordNumber;
        public Word(String wordLower, String wordCapital, String wordSpecielLower, String wordSpecielCapital, String wordNumber) {
            super();
            this.wordLower = wordLower;
            this.wordCapital = wordCapital;
            this.wordSpecielLower = wordSpecielLower;
            this.wordSpecielCapital = wordSpecielCapital;
            this.wordNumber = wordNumber;
        }
        public String toString() {
            return wordLower + wordCapital + wordNumber + wordSpecielLower + wordSpecielCapital;    //通过这个方法进行顺序的控制
        }
    }

73.Redmine97742:(设置)设置情境模式预览音量能后台播放，且播放的时候来电，播放铃声和来电铃声能同时播放

解决方案：
在退出的时候暂停播放
alps/packages/apps/Settings/src/com/mediatek/audioprofile/AudioProfileSettings.java
    public void onPause() {
        super.onPause();
        SagerealVolumePreference alarm_volume_perference = (SagerealVolumePreference)findPreference(KEY_ALARM_VOLUME);
        SagerealVolumePreference ring_volume_perference = (SagerealVolumePreference)findPreference(KEY_RING_VOLUME);
        if(alarm_volume_perference != null){
            alarm_volume_perference.stopPlaying();  //在onPause的时候停止播放
        }
        if(ring_volume_perference != null){
            ring_volume_perference.stopPlaying();   //在onPause的时候停止播放
        }
        mProfileManager.listenAudioProfie(mListener, AudioProfileListener.LISTEN_NONE);
    }

